title: CreativeMarket - Hansen - HTML5 Template
description:
Hansen is HTML5 Responsive Template based on Bootstrap 3, with a clean minimalist design. Template is usable for more types of websites, landing pages, product sites or start-up websites. It comes in three variants - Static Image Background, Image Slider and Youtube Video Background. Of course, the template is very easily customizable.
